Mabel WORKMAN, as County Treasurer of Smith County, Kansas, et al. v. FIRST NATIONAL BANK OF SMITH CENTER, KANSAS. No. 220. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. June 4, 1930. Relihan & Relihan^ of Smith Center, Kan., for appellants. Wheeler, Brewster & Hunt, of Topeka, Kan., for appellee.

Before LEWIS, COTTERAL, and PHILLIPS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed June 4,1930, on stipulation.
